@startuml
state WaitingForCard
state EnterPin
state VerifyingPin
state SuccessfulPinVerification
state Options
state WithdrawalRequest
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state DispensingCash
state PrintingReceipt
state CompletedTransaction
state ReturningCard
state Resetting

WaitingForCard --> EnterPin: CardInserted
EnterPin --> VerifyingPin: PinEntered
VerifyingPin --> SuccessfulPinVerification: ValidPin
SuccessfulPinVerification --> Options: PinVerified
Options --> WithdrawalRequest: ApproveWithdrawal
WithdrawalRequest --> ProcessingWithdrawal: StartProcessing
ProcessingWithdrawal --> DispensingCash: CashDispensed
DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt: ReceiptPrinted
PrintingReceipt --> CompletedTransaction: ReceiptPrinted
CompletedTransaction --> ReturningCard: CardReturned
CompletedTransaction --> Resetting: SystemReset
Resetting --> WaitingForCard: ReadyForNextUser
@enduml
